title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 3
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Following up a strong week 1, Rico Bosco is in the lead for the Pat Hill Trophy. Also, after 7 years we finally got a new logo, shoutout to Trigs!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
